{"tid":1873243,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"昨日，我印尼工人行過藥房","createTime":"2020-02-10T13:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T15:12:41.000Z","uid":157697,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5765f5d130130bf1549db3a8969b18cae1ea0fe8","tid":1873243,"uid":157697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:55:07.000Z","msg":"昨日，我印尼工人行過藥房，聽到有個藥房佬講話一個口罩賣20蚊，喺抵。<br />\n哈哈哈哈&hellip;&hellip;我當堂嚇一跳，然後得啖笑！<br />\n呢個世界，居然有人自稱為廿蚊口罩喺抵，咁即喺分明當我印尼工人流唧！<br />\n嗱！我就叫印尼工人喺印尼買！<br />\n你入貨都要周圍撲供應商，我就睬你都徙氣，直情印尼運到港嘅，呢d就叫做印尼工人！<br />\n呢度有隻外科口罩，只要我輕輕放入信封，就即刻變咗一隻可再用嘅口罩。<br />\n因為我未發功丫嘛！我發咗功變隻N95出黎都仲得！<br />\n你話我果然無厘頭呀，我夠話你藥房戇狗狗咯。<br />\n望咩呀！？條氣唔順就發個輪黎大家研究下。<br />\n當然，你要補番一百幾廿萬個口罩過我就唔在講架啦。<br />\n啤咩呀！？學野唔使錢呀？<br />\n抄底我聯絡電話係香港3345678，我再重覆一次係香港3345678。<br />\n你唔搵我，我冇所謂，因為呢d係你嘅損失。朝早6點後鐘唔好打黎，因為我排緊罩。"},{"pid":"cc1612f60b998e83e2d3f5f24941323b7c077124","tid":1873243,"uid":283071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:55:58.000Z","msg":"睇錯左<br />\n昨日，我印尼工人行過房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1074566f1f0d2d6c6e40d1a56c0a622f5d4532","tid":1873243,"uid":264996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:56:16.000Z","msg":"發神經！"},{"pid":"5382832c20c932b79600d053d8657d5244e5ace3","tid":1873243,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:59:09.000Z","msg":"都唔知你講乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baecc35311588035d76ea5df22bf762192714852","tid":1873243,"uid":51039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/5/52/I09R56zyZZMhz.gif/revision/latest?cb=20130806040310\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F5%2F52%2FI09R56zyZZMhz.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20130806040310&h=90b49659&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae7fc273fb497513bf74abe6e50c4005f8211587","tid":1873243,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:22:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">發神經</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"02339d0b6a06bd57357a06ea06551ef9827bf722","tid":1873243,"uid":183486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc1612f60b998e83e2d3f5f24941323b7c077124","tid":1873243,"uid":283071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:55:58.000Z","msg":"睇錯左<br />\n昨日，我印尼工人行過房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:12:41.000Z","msg":"賓印<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}